snippet.title: Best VGM 899 - Lunar : Eternal Blue - The Last Battle
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 388 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ej4PiY8AESE

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Sega CD
Lunar: Eternal Blue (1994)
The Last Battle
Noriyuki Iwadare
